{"tid":2108971,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特朗普簽《香港自治法》兼取消特殊特遇　指很多人離開香港失競爭優勢","createTime":"2020-07-15T02:11:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-15T02:56:51.000Z","uid":60281,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c22df4142dca01b2b00ed11ef5ef1eeb1c016be3","tid":2108971,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T02:11:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n特朗普在白宮玫瑰園召開記者會，他說中國政府對香港強加壓迫性的國安法，必須追究責任，又說自己不打算同國家主席習近平通話。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普說，香港不再享有特殊特遇、經濟優惠，也不會對港輸出敏感科技設備：「香港的待遇將同中國一樣。」<br />\n<br />\n「大家都看到（香港）發生了什麼事，情況不好。他們（港人）的自由和權利被剝奪。......我的看法是，香港將不能與自由市場競爭。」「我相信會有很多人離開香港。」又說美國將會有更多機遇，「因為我們剛失去了一個對手。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E7%B0%BD-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%87%AA%E6%B2%BB%E6%B3%95-%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E7%89%B9%E6%AE%8A%E7%89%B9%E9%81%87-%E5%BE%88%E5%A4%9A%E4%BA%BA%E9%9B%A2%E9%96%8B%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%B1%E7%AB%B6%E7%88%AD%E5%84%AA%E5%8B%A2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25E7%25B0%25BD-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E5%258F%2596%25E6%25B6%2588%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%25AE%258A%25E7%2589%25B9%25E9%2581%2587-%25E5%25BE%2588%25E5%25A4%259A%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%259B%25A2%25E9%2596%258B%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E7%25AB%25B6%25E7%2588%25AD%25E5%2584%25AA%25E5%258B%25A2%2F&d=fc%2FsVbAXSk%2FqMRyYewxCuMF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=e53bc063\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25E7%25B0%25BD-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E5%258F%2596%25E6%25B6%2588%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%25AE%258A%25E7